      "span_text": "For example, in a recently published paper about a knockout mouse which is deficient of iGb 3 synthase, the authors had no method capable of detecting thymic iGb 3 in wild-type mice; therefore, it is impossible to prove that iGb 3 is indeed missing in the thymus of iGb 3 synthase knockout mice [CITATION_1] .",
